{"tid":1950490,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"誰洗了她的腦袋？（上） - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-03-30T11:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T11:36:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"891dbc42638be6591ff723d228b56c1fcc3a0954","tid":1950490,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:08:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200330/20889903/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200330%2F20889903%2F&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2TizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=ee58dbe7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200330%2F20889903%2F&h=a84cb665\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200330/20889903/</a><br />\n<br />\n誰洗了她的腦袋？（上） - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200330/large/1585464991_96a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200330%2Flarge%2F1585464991_96a2.jpg&h=cc1965dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n互聯網<br />\n<br />\n朋友M打電話來，瘟疫流行，大家都居家避疫，不愛下廚的M也被迫做煮婦。一開始大家交流煮食心得，倒也聊得開心。後來她嘆氣說，「唉，這場病不知要延續多久？」我說，「唉！中國輸出病毒，把全世界搞得立立亂&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\nM突然反面，語氣變得嚴厲，在電話另一端喝斥我：「你怎麼賴中國？中國是全世界控制病毒做得最快、最好的國家。你不怪其他國家你去怪中國？」<br />\n<br />\n我問她，「記得病毒發源地在武漢嗎？1月23號武漢就封城了。當時中國官方媒體都承認華南海鮮城的野味巿場惹禍&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n「你不要再說了！」M阻止我再往下說，「我不需要跟你爭拗這個問題。誰也不知道病毒究竟由哪個國家傳出，全世界都有責任，不要甚麼都賴中國。」<br />\n<br />\n說話至此，我知道我和這個朋友緣盡了。我沒再跟她「爭拗」，我不動聲色地說「拜拜」，然後收線。<br />\n<br />\n我住在Calgary，一個安靜的城巿，靜得能聽到門外雪地上野兔跳躍的聲音。那跳躍聲在一片靜寂中，竟然如鼓，敲擊着我的耳膜。<br />\n<br />\n我先是被無邊無際的憤怒淹沒，之後，失望之情代替了我的憤怒。<br />\n<br />\nM是我到Calgary之後最早結識的朋友。她比我年長一大截，我們的共同興趣不多，但我眼中的她，像是一個姑姐、姨媽似的人物，是可以信賴的親戚。 <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk"},{"pid":"8004a43fa3edf7ba7eeea3c99fd47d53d92b1631","tid":1950490,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T11:36:35.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}